ly\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"things you must do in Italy (opens in a new tab)\">things you must do in Italy<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full vertical-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135822\/things-to-do-rome-colosseum.jpg\" alt=\"things to do rome colosseum\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"things to do rome colosseum\" class=\"wp-image-13947 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1484px) 100vw, 1484px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135822\/things-to-do-rome-colosseum.jpg 1484w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135822\/things-to-do-rome-colosseum-300x388.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135822\/things-to-do-rome-colosseum-600x776.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135822\/things-to-do-rome-colosseum-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135822\/things-to-do-rome-colosseum-464x600.jpg 464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135822\/things-to-do-rome-colosseum-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135822\/things-to-do-rome-colosseum-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135822\/things-to-do-rome-colosseum-126x163.jpg 126w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135822\/things-to-do-rome-colosseum-139x180.jpg 139w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135822\/things-to-do-rome-colosseum-594x768.jpg 594w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135822\/things-to-do-rome-colo