o visit the Arch of Constantine, located next to the Colosseum. <\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-full\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135921\/things-to-do-rome-italy-Colosseum.jpg\" alt=\"things to do rome italy Colosseum\"><\/noscript><img width=\"450\" height=\"316\" alt=\"things to do rome italy Colosseum\" class=\"wp-image-13917 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1920px) 100vw, 1920px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135921\/things-to-do-rome-italy-Colosseum.jpg 1920w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135921\/things-to-do-rome-italy-Colosseum-300x210.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135921\/things-to-do-rome-italy-Colosseum-600x421.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135921\/things-to-do-rome-italy-Colosseum-450x316.jpg 450w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135921\/things-to-do-rome-italy-Colosseum-800x561.jpg 800w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135921\/things-to-do-rome-italy-Colosseum-1080x758.jpg 1080w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135921\/things-to-do-rome-italy-Colosseum-30x21.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135921\/things-to-do-rome-italy-Colosseum-163x114.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135921\/things-to-do-rome-italy-Colosseum-257x180.jpg 257w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135921\/things-to-do-rome-italy-Colosseum-768x539.jpg 768w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135921\/things-to-do-rome-italy-Colosseum-1024x718.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/w