class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--attractions\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/go\/tickets-colosseum\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Get your tickets here (opens in a new tab)\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Get your tickets here<\/a>.<\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>Join a tour and learn more about the area instead of walking around and seeing just ruins.<br><br><strong>Getting hungry? <\/strong>Have a finger-licking good lunch at Humus Bistrot. It is near the next thing to do in Rome.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/rome-guide-spring-626x810.jpg\" alt=\"rome guide spring\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"rome guide spring\" data-id=\"13914\" data-link=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=13914\" class=\"wp-image-13914 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 626px) 100vw, 626px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135932\/rome-guide-spring-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135932\/rome-guide-spring-300x388.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135932\/rome-guide-spring-600x776.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135932\/rome-guide-spring-261x