ad block-pinterest__image\" alt=\"9 Best Things To Do in Rome, Italy (3-day Guide)\" height=\"600\" width=\"373\">\n                    <\/div>\n                <\/div>\n            <\/a><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<p>The first part is free to visit and to visit the top an entrance ticket is required. Sitting on the monument\/stair steps is not allowed.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Also read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/italy\/cinque-terre\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">The Colorful Villages of Cinque Terre, Italy<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/things-to-do-rome-Altare-Della-Patria-626x810.jpg\" alt=\"things to do rome Altare DellaPatria\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"things to do rome Altare DellaPatria\" data-id=\"13911\" data-link=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=13911\" class=\"wp-image-13911 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 626px) 100vw, 626px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135942\/things-to-do-rome-Altare-Della-Patria-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135942\/things-to-do-rome-Altare-Della-Patria-300x388.