cover on foot. Everything is quite close, especially when it&#x2019;s spread over 3 days. Expect to walk around 4 km per day during a Rome City Trip. <\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--hotels \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--hotels\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/go\/rome-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Find all hotels in Rome<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div><\/div><\/div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-group\"><div class=\"wp-block-group__inner-container\">\n<h3>4. Castel Sant&#x2019;Angelo<\/h3>\n\n\n\n<p>Castel Sant&#x2019;Angelo is a unique round-shaped military building. The five floors inside, connected by a spiral stair goes all the way to the roof terrace. A perfect spot for taking photos. Make sure to be on time to avoid the crowd as tours start around 9 AM.<\/p>\n\n\n<div class=\"block-link block-link--readmore \">\n                <div class=\"block-link__container\">\n\n                    <div class=\"salt-icon__container\">\n                        <span class=\"salt-icon salt-icon--readmore\"><\/span>\n                        <svg class=\"icon icon-round-shape\"><use xlink:href=\"#icon-round-shape\"><\/use><\/svg>\n                    <\/div>\n\n                    <p><strong>Also read:<\/strong> <a href=\"https:\/\/www.saltinourhair.com\/italy\/florence\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" aria-label=\"Things to do in Florence (opens in a new tab)\">24 hours of best Things to do in Florence<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image vertical-image\"><div class=