<p><a href=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/go\/rome-all\/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" data-rich-text-format-boundary=\"true\">Find all hotels in Rome<\/a><\/p>\n\n\n                <\/div>\n            <\/div>\n\n\n<p><strong>Pro tip:<\/strong> If you are planning to visit the Vatican Museum, you can go directly to St. Peter&#x2019;s Basilica via the museum and skip the line.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image\"><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/rome-guide-St.-Peters-Basilica-1065x810.jpg\" alt=\"rome guide St. Peter's Basilica\"><\/noscript><img width=\"444\" height=\"338\" alt=\"rome guide St. Peter's Basilica\" class=\"wp-image-13933 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 1065px) 100vw, 1065px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135839\/rome-guide-St.-Peters-Basilica-1065x810.jpg 1065w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135839\/rome-guide-St.-Peters-Basilica-300x228.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135839\/rome-guide-St.-Peters-Basilica-600x456.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135839\/rome-guide-St.-Peters-Basilica-444x338.jpg 444w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135839\/rome-guide-St.-Peters-Basilica-789x600.jpg 789w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135839\/rome-guide-St.-Peters-Basilica-30x23.jpg 30w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135839\/rome-guide-St.-Peters-Basilica-163x124.jpg 163w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135839\/rome-guide-St.-Peters-Basilica-237x180.jpg 237w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135839\/rome-guide-St.-Peters-Basilica-768x584.jpg 768w, https:\/\