rists having a good time in the park. You can rent bikes to go around but it great to walk around by yourself. You can easily reach the park by metro or bus.<\/p>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><div class=\"image-wrapper\"><div class=\"fake-image\"><\/div><noscript><img src=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/things-to-do-rome-villa-borghese-park-626x810.jpg\" alt=\"things to do rome villa borghese park\"><\/noscript><img width=\"261\" height=\"338\" alt=\"things to do rome villa borghese park\" data-id=\"13924\" data-link=\"https:\/\/saltinourhair.com\/?attachment_id=13924\" class=\"wp-image-13924 lazypreload\" data-sizes=\"(max-width: 626px) 100vw, 626px\" data-srcset=\"https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135908\/things-to-do-rome-villa-borghese-park-626x810.jpg 626w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135908\/things-to-do-rome-villa-borghese-park-300x388.jpg 300w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135908\/things-to-do-rome-villa-borghese-park-600x776.jpg 600w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135908\/things-to-do-rome-villa-borghese-park-261x338.jpg 261w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135908\/things-to-do-rome-villa-borghese-park-464x600.jpg 464w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135908\/things-to-do-rome-villa-borghese-park-23x30.jpg 23w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135908\/things-to-do-rome-villa-borghese-park-126x163.jpg 126w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135908\/things-to-do-rome-villa-borghese-park-139x180.jpg 139w, https:\/\/static.saltinourhair.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2019\/04\/23135908\/things-to-do-rome-villa-borghese-park-594x768.j